    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Gunabopicobia spp. G. masalaje Kaszewska et al. 2014, female (A – D). A, hypostomal apex and distal part of movable cheliceral digits; B, peritreme; C, proximal end of movable cheliceral digit; D, solenidia of leg I. Male (E – G). E, hypostomal apex and distal part of movable cheliceral digits; F, peritremes; G, genito-anal region. G. zumpti (Lawrence, 1959), female (H, I). H, peritreme; I, solenidia of leg I." ;
